Package: UIEM3App
Title: User-Integrated Energy Management Maturity Model (UI-EM3) App
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Raquel",
           family = "Lima",
           email = "raquel.lima@universityofgalway.ie",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    A Shiny web application developed to assist decision-makers in companies, universities, and schools
    by providing an evaluation of energy management maturity through the integration of user perspectives.
    It was derived from a PhD research project at the University of Galway. The application processes survey
    responses, calculates maturity levels based on indicators, criteria, and topics, and offers insights
    through comparisons over time, settings, and audiences.
